Qinghua University Commemorates Leading Scientist
BEIJING , November 22 ( Xinhua ) -- Qinghua University , one of China 's most prestigious institution of higher education , today hosted commemorative activities to mark the 100th birth anniversary of Ye Qisun , a leading Chinese physicist .
Ye studying at Qinghua from 1913 to 1918 , and became a physics professor of the university in 1925 after a six-year study program in the United States .
Ye worked as professsor from 1925 to 1952 and taught dozens of famous experts and scientists in the field of physics , including two Nobel Prize winners and over 60 Chinese academicians .
More than 100 of Ye 's friends and students attended the event .
